name: Between The Beginning and The End
description:
As we born into this world, the purity lies deep inside human heart. While doubt fill every single on of us, in the end, we shall remember the end of us; Death. Between the end and the beginning, we shall remember, time has taken its toll on you; the line that crack your face.

The artwork is inspired by the progress of life that every human being been through. The baby represent the beginning of human journey as they're born into this world. The skull represent death as the end of human life. The color blue, yellow and gold represent doubt, hope and purity. The line in the face represent time as the person getting old.
